rows.label: xs08160100_MSG0001
rows.name:
There's no excuse. This wouldn't have happened
if I didn't order my men to leave their posts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08160100_MSG0002
rows.name: You were just trying to help. It's okay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08160100_MSG0003
rows.name:
We should count ourselves lucky
we ended up with so few casualties.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08160100_MSG0004
rows.name: Sorry to break up the love-in.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08160100_MSG0006
rows.name:
There must be SOMETHING to that Skell
if they were this worried about it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08160100_MSG0008
rows.name: (The bigger question is how they even knew we had it...)[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08160100_MSG0009
rows.name: (And how did they know exactly where we were keeping it...)[ST:wait ]
